column1: Table 3a: Long-term international immigration to the UK among the top ten highest contributing non-EU+ nationalities as of YE December 2024, by reason for immigration,
using new approach to producing migration estimates [definition 4] [notes 4, 5, 6, 7, 9 and 13]
Notes and definitions are referred to in this table. The text for these can be found in the corresponding worksheets.
Some shorthand is used in this table, P = provisional, R = revised, YE = Year Ending and EU = European Union.
